{"word":"G968 - βῆμα - bēma - bay'-ma - Judgment-seat","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βῆμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bēma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>bay'-ma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Judgment-seat"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நியாயாசனம், சிங்காசனம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a step, pace, the official seat of a judge"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From the base of <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a>; a <i>step</i>, that is, <i>foot breath</i>; by implication a <i>rostrum</i>, that is, <i>tribunal:</i> - judgment-seat, set [foot] on, throne."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}